text: The Fifth Season is a 1997 Iranian French comedy movie directed by Rafi Pitts and starring Parviz Poorhosseini, Shah Ali Sarkhani, Roya Nunhali, Gulab Adineh, Qurban Najafi. == Other websites == * Category:1997 comedy movies Category:Iranian movies Category:French comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Rafi Pitts
